{"tid":1238833,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中国停止向WTO提出「承認中国市場經濟地位」爭端訴訟","createTime":"2019-06-18T03:11:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-18T04:07:17.000Z","uid":184679,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"5aa730d3fd7d975cbeeffca2b5c53a587320aefe","tid":1238833,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T03:11:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2924561/org/7b8c5103abba7a464eb772ababdf3bf5.jpg/CIxbDc6XXNLwQgVJrBWzQhL-vAZH7PVOK4gX9SuIF_U?v=w1600r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2924561%2Forg%2F7b8c5103abba7a464eb772ababdf3bf5.jpg%2FCIxbDc6XXNLwQgVJrBWzQhL-vAZH7PVOK4gX9SuIF_U%3Fv%3Dw1600r16_9&h=d574be42&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n世貿組織（WTO）爭端解決小組星期一（6月17日）表示，中國已停止向世貿組織提出的「承認中國市場經濟地位」爭端的訴訟。<br />\n<br />\n這意味著中國必須要接受歐盟和美國對中國廉價商品繼續施加的「反傾銷」關稅。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">據路透社消息，一位接近此爭端的貿易官員說，世貿組織的大部分裁決都對北京不利，因此北京選擇在世貿組織正式的結果出來之前停止爭端訴訟。這位官員說，「他們敗訴了很多，他們甚至不想讓世界看到爭端解決小組（裁決）的理由。」</span><br />\n<br />\n在沒有世貿組織做出對北京有利的裁決的情況下，歐盟和美國能不理會中國宣稱的他們的商品價格公平，繼續對廉價中國商品加徵關稅。<br />\n<br />\n中國堅持認為，根據2001年加入WTO規定，中國在加入世貿組織15年後應該被認定為「市場經濟地位」。中國常駐世貿組織代表張向晨在世貿組織2017年的一次聽證上說，「中國認為，對於這個簡單和明確無誤的條約用詞，不可能再有其他似是而非的解讀了」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B/341736/%E6%89%BF%E8%AA%8D%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%B8%82%E5%A0%B4%E7%B6%93%E6%BF%9F%E5%9C%B0%E4%BD%8D-%E7%94%B3%E8%A8%B4%E6%A1%88-%E4%B8%AD%E6%96%B9%E5%BE%9Ewto%E6%92%A4%E8%A8%B4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%2F341736%2F%25E6%2589%25BF%25E8%25AA%258D%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25B8%2582%25E5%25A0%25B4%25E7%25B6%2593%25E6%25BF%259F%25E5%259C%25B0%25E4%25BD%258D-%25E7%2594%25B3%25E8%25A8%25B4%25E6%25A1%2588-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E6%2596%25B9%25E5%25BE%259Ewto%25E6%2592%25A4%25E8%25A8%25B4&d=7EcP4%2BvGpl6inSsjOqiUXllsl4SrcEEyWLual4COuMU%3D&h=d2974c6a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B/341736/%E6%89%BF%E8%AA%8D%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%B8%82%E5%A0%B4%E7%B6%93%E6%BF%9F%E5%9C%B0%E4%BD%8D-%E7%94%B3%E8%A8%B4%E6%A1%88-%E4%B8%AD%E6%96%B9%E5%BE%9Ewto%E6%92%A4%E8%A8%B4</a>"},{"pid":"342b9b75a00b2abef119f7f05b0cb28f0f07458d","tid":1238833,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T04:04:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be06ed1ed8c07f4e937033226a02ef599ceef00f","tid":1238833,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T04:05:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d71327f0488a1cdb3fb145fa7c7e2bdbe32c4624","tid":1238833,"uid":215928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T04:07:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />中国又赢"}]}